 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jun 11, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Gracious God, <br></br>
who knows us better <br></br>
than we know ourselves,
</p>

 <p>
Forgive me, <br></br>
when I quickly judge <br></br>
a harsh word, <br></br>
or impolite response <br></br>
without knowing <br></br>
the full story.
</p>

 <p>
Everyone has a story, <br></br>
and every encounter <br></br>
affects the plot, <br></br>
and each moment <br></br>
is another opportunity <br></br>
to transform the tale <br></br>
from hopeless tragedy <br></br>
to divine beauty.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>



